---
title: Prosciutto-Wrapped Lamb & Cheesy Mash with Garlicky Veggies & Hollandaise Sauce
description: Treat yourself with this tender and moist lamb that’s been gently wrapped by salty prosciutto. Following closely behind on the
theme of decadence, there’s a rich peppercorn-hollandaise sauce and creamy mash to soak it up. Kick your feet up because it’s
time to dig into a restaurant-quality dish in the comfort of your own home.

*We’ve replaced the baby rainbow carrots in this recipe with carrots due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
